{"tid":1011121,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呻自己矮? 有增高手術。呻自己樣衰? 有整容手術。","createTime":"2019-02-06T13:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T11:27:42.000Z","uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b1325642553ecb632299005be208e47d00d73ff1","tid":1011121,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:41:09.000Z","msg":"儲到錢，可以接受瞓醫院等復原就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整容一兩個禮拜就得，增高半年至一年啦<br />\n解決辦法根本有晒，問題係你願唔願意投資時間金錢同埋忍受痛苦去改變自己<br />\n唔願意嘅唔駛再呻，接受自己矮、樣衰或者兩樣都齊嘅事實算啦<br />\n最多都係呻諗唔到辦法搵/慳呢筆錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7dc96b7a7951e1193bc5a93e90f47aa7b2ff0f","tid":1011121,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T00:59:05.000Z","msg":"唔好為咗自己外表問題一日到黑喺度呻<br />\n搵辦法徹底解決"},{"pid":"9f7d2f063abf953eaee29adb370ac2db614b2e80","tid":1011121,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"唔好諗咩違反自然定律，起碼好撚過一世唔撚敢出街"},{"pid":"04b72e296f301e3edfed4e4e0745a2d756c7c9b9","tid":1011121,"uid":30042,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:18:24.000Z","msg":"巴打講得好，等我一儲夠錢我就去做手術<br />\n<br />\nd人成日話咩內在美緊要嗰d全部都係搵笨柒，當你係又樣衰又矮嘅時候你就知道有幾無助"},{"pid":"8ccdeb9541d85c1f001b80ac25de78e8073d9161","tid":1011121,"uid":16767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"邊有得增高呀 増完仲行唔行到"},{"pid":"30e539f6f0fb260b27bbd6acda6d120078ec1236","tid":1011121,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8ccdeb9541d85c1f001b80ac25de78e8073d9161","tid":1011121,"uid":16767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"邊有得增高呀 増完仲行唔行到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"行唔到係因為冇按足醫生/物理治療師指示去做"},{"pid":"9c7044f7da8d90793d641201e6a927c6e5885c48","tid":1011121,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:59:56.